# ============================================================
# LOCATION DETAIL POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: policy
domain: detail
subdomain: location-detail
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Defines policy rules for location detail.

policy_focus:
- open versus restricted zone disclosure
- historical layout retention
- facility-internal access disclosure limits
- closure-state disclosure rules

disclosure_matrix:
- open_zone: public allowed
- facility_internal: internal only
- restricted_zone: public denied
- historical_layout: history mode only

validation_rules:
- restricted or closed zones must not be classified as open public detail.
- historical layouts must remain labeled as historical.
